Author: fabscarbs
Text: Same here, I can’t start university with the thought of having to deal with all this bs still. It’s been VERY hard so far but I’m optimistic :) keep going xx

Author: NewBullMoose
Text: Good luck! Your ED will tell you that you're better off alone... you'll start off just eating alone, then that will gradually spread to other things until you wind up with nobody to reach out to, nobody to hold you accountable. Don't listen to it. I did and now I have no support system at college and it just enables my ED behaviors.
